{"tid":1669543,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"「正視聽」要支持加泰嘅唔係舉集會，而係香港人要做個成功嘅榜樣","createTime":"2019-10-22T15:23:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T00:43:23.000Z","uid":92476,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"fbc398ffa12c404e69077f57b65ccb099075484c","tid":1669543,"uid":92476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T15:23:27.000Z","msg":"加泰嘅核心價值係加獨，唔係話民主，啲人開集會話支持人哋個啲只係擦波邊，都唔係人地最想要嘅訴求<br />\n<br />\n逆地而處，如果加泰人開集會話支持你反警暴乜乜乜，但唔好意思，唔係支持你港獨架，唔好誤會。你估啲港獨派會唔會好care你個集會<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咪得班加泰和理非開心一陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">加泰要嘅，係Make a new Hong Kong! 而你，香港人，要支持加泰就係成功爭取到五大訴求，令全世界最大嘅強權屈服香港人，回應訴求，你爭取唔到五大訴求，加泰會唔會向失敗者學習？采你都傻啦，仲得閒理你咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n一句到尾，要支持加泰，你打贏到全球最大強国，就係最好嘅支持，輸咗就入集中營支持啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f52f879cfcce3fc1749a3894806973bcb057518b","tid":1669543,"uid":82955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T15:23:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1665303/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1665303/page/1</a><br />\n[文宣升級] 郵差叔叔送信純熟將文宣迅速送出!<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4H03stW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4H03stW.png&h=37a4782b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ae0OUGc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAe0OUGc.jpg&h=70e794a5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"25800f2f505cc5cdd6fbd60b87a569c3464a6222","tid":1669543,"uid":92476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T15:25:03.000Z","msg":"不服來辯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c648c17948b712544152d937c2230c4a236d10a4","tid":1669543,"uid":92476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite